reviewText: This did not work in our dvd player but kept giving us an error reading. Very very disappointed.

This DVD is labeled "all-region," but is in PAL format rather than the US standard NTSC.  It works on my computer, but not on my DVD player or my Blu-ray player.

It contains about 60 minutes of short Rolie Polie Olie cartoons, and they're all cute and fun to watch.  I just wish there had been more information on the Amazon description page about the format.
I chose thi item and a few others because you can not find them in stores. The other 2 worked, this one did not and I have not had time to mess with getting it returned.
